  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Oshi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, you've learned that lying is the truest form of love, having no true concept of it for yourself. Your eyes take on a starry pattern of a color of your choice. When you would socially interact with a creature that can see your eyes, you can use Deception in place of a required skill check. Alternatively, when casting a Genjutsu with the Visual or Auditory keywords, you can ignore any HS or CS components. You can use these effects a combined number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus per rest.</p><p>Additionally, you gain advantage on saving throws against the Charmed and Berserk conditions, and creatures have disadvantage on Insight checks made against you. At 7th level, you cannot be Charmed.</p>",
